Privacy Policy for Deluxe Muslim Companion
Last Updated: July 1, 2026
Welcome to Deluxe Muslim Companion ("the App"). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information the App uses, how it is used, and your rights.
Information We Collect
Location Information
With your permission, the App accesses your device's location to:
Display accurate prayer times.
Calculate the direction of the Qibla.
Find nearby mosques.
Find nearby halal restaurants.
Your location is processed only to provide these features.
Personal Information
The App does not require you to create an account and does not intentionally collect personal information such as:
Name
Email address
Phone number
Postal address
unless you choose to provide it when contacting support.
How We Use Information
Information is used solely to provide and improve the App's features, including:
Prayer time calculations
Qibla direction
Nearby mosque search
Nearby halal restaurant search
Language preferences
App functionality and reliability
Third-Party Services
The App may use third-party services, including:
Apple Maps (for maps, directions, and nearby locations)
Prayer time data providers
Apple's built-in location services
These services operate under their own privacy policies.
Data Storage
The App may store certain preferences locally on your device, such as:
Selected language
Tasbih counter progress
App settings
This information remains on your device unless you delete the App.
Analytics
If analytics are enabled in future versions, anonymous usage information may be collected to improve the App. No personally identifiable information will be sold.
Data Sharing
We do not sell your personal information.
We do not share your personal information with third parties except where necessary to provide App functionality or where required by law.
Children's Privacy
The App is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect personal information from children.
Security
Reasonable measures are taken to protect information processed by the App. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is completely secure.
Your Rights
Depending on your country or region, you may have rights regarding your personal information, including the right to:
Request access to information
Request correction
Request deletion where applicable
Changes to This Policy
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any updates will be published on this page.
Contact
